text: @UPSHelp what’s wrong with your UPS Mychoice service. I’ve been calling you about this issue for months and NO ONE can fix it! I have a package for my household member with the EXACT SAME ADDRESS listed on my account and you’re still saying it doesn’t match! It’s been months!
